)
jonathandturner fixed some issues with external args (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1687] #1687
), remove per-item commands (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1685] #1685
), added it-expansion (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1681] #1681
, 
