), added a 
``not-in:``
 operator (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1661] #1661
)
andrasio added new commands for working with tables (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1686] #1686
), added a command for checking for emptiness (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1665] #1665
), added more functionality to 
``str``
 (
