)
JosephTLyons and mhmdanas improved our .gitignore (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1691] #1691
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1684] #1684
)
mhmdanas also cleaned up the operator parsing code (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1683] #1683
)
JosephTLyons added showing filesizes for symlinks themselves (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1680] #1680
)
quebin31 replaced 'ichwh' for 'which' in a few places to improve auto-cd times (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1672] #1672
), fixed cd'ing to symlinked directories (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1651] #1651
)
rimathia made 
``trim``
 work for all cells rather than just strings (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1664] #1664
), made 
``--help``
 work in more places (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1659] #1659
)
thegedge cleaned up some of the auto-cd logic (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1660] #1660
)
aeshirey added a 
``from-eml``
 command (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1656] #1656
)
siedentop improved docs for 
``str``
 (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1653] #1653
)
